Call TEXTE(6028,GBOUTS) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(12276,GBOUTP) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(16134,GBOUTA) From OBJDIV
Onkey 129 Titled GBOUT1 Call B1_CRY(zc) From W1ORG1
Onkey   2 Titled GBOUTS Call S_CRY(zc) From W1ORG1
Onkey 144 Titled GBOUTP Call P_CRY(zc) From W1ORG1
